
  <sn><md>### Weathering of Amphibole Family

**General Formula:** $\{\mathrm{X_{7\text{-}8}(Si_4O_{11})_2}\}$ where $\mathrm{X = Ca, Na, Mg, Fe, Al}$

Chemically, `amphiboles are analogous to pyroxene`. However, because pyroxenes possess more basic characteristics, they `weather faster than amphiboles`.
</md></sn>
